A NICE, JEWISH GUY.

42:26.678 --> 42:29.581
- HEY, DEB, LISTEN TO THIS.

42:29.615 --> 42:32.350
"AND THEN THE UNTHINKABLE
HAPPENED.

42:32.383 --> 42:34.653
"DREW BOYD,
HERO TO MILLIONS OF FANS,

42:34.686 --> 42:38.590
"PLANTED ONE ON CHANNEL FIVE'S
QUEER GUY.

42:38.624 --> 42:40.692
"IT WAS THE KISS HEARD
ROUND THE WORLD.

42:40.726 --> 42:42.060
"THE QUESTION IS,
NOW WHAT?

42:42.093 --> 42:43.962
"WILL MR. BOYD STILL
BE CALLED A HERO,

42:43.995 --> 42:46.264
"OR WILL HE BE CALLED A LOT
OF LESS FLATTERING THINGS?

42:46.297 --> 42:48.066
"IT DOESN'T REALLY MATTER.

42:48.099 --> 42:49.334
"WHAT MATTERS IS,

42:49.367 --> 42:51.236
"DREW BOYD HAS
SCORED A TOUCHDOWN

42:51.269 --> 42:53.939
FOR PERSONAL COURAGE
AND HONESTY."

42:53.972 --> 42:55.073
- YES!

42:55.106 --> 42:58.109
[distant shouting]

43:00.912 --> 43:02.681
- WILL YOU
LET THE MAN IN?

43:02.714 --> 43:03.815
- DREW...
- THANK YOU.

43:03.849 --> 43:05.116
[indistinct chatter]

43:05.150 --> 43:07.118
[door shuts]

43:07.152 --> 43:08.987
- I'M SORRY ABOUT THIS.

43:09.020 --> 43:11.022
- IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT, HONEY.

43:11.056 --> 43:14.225
DO THEY HAVE TO TRAMPLE
MY FUCKING ROSE BED?

43:14.259 --> 43:15.861
- WELL, WAIT TILL
YOU READ THIS.

43:15.894 --> 43:18.630
YOU'RE GOING
TO BE SO PROUD.

43:18.664 --> 43:20.732
- I'VE BEEN SUSPENDED.

43:20.766 --> 43:22.734
- WHAT?

43:22.768 --> 43:24.002
WHY?

43:24.035 --> 43:25.837
YOU WEREN'T
DRIVING DRUNK,

43:25.871 --> 43:27.639
YOU DIDN'T RAPE ANYBODY,

43:27.673 --> 43:28.874
YOU WEREN'T MAKING
ILLEGAL BETS.

43:28.907 --> 43:29.975
ALL YOU DID WAS...
- DEB...

43:30.008 --> 43:33.078
- WHAT?
- WE KNOW WHAT HE DID.

43:37.415 --> 43:41.286
- MY COACH SAYS
IT'S FOR MY OWN GOOD.

43:41.319 --> 43:45.123
IN CASE MY TEAMMATES
TRY TO INJURE ME.

43:45.156 --> 43:48.059
- I THOUGHT YOU WERE SUPPOSED
TO LOOK OUT FOR EACH OTHER.

43:50.762 --> 43:52.964
- SO DID I.

44:00.071 --> 44:02.874
- YOU'RE BEING
AWFULLY DILIGENT.

44:02.908 --> 44:05.677
- IT'S OUR HOME.

44:05.711 --> 44:08.046
I WANT EVERYTHING
TO BE PERFECT.

44:08.079 --> 44:11.750
- YOU'RE IN IT, THAT'S
PERFECT ENOUGH FOR ME.

44:11.783 --> 44:14.019
- THAT IS THE MOST CLOYINGLY
SENTIMENTAL REMARK

44:14.052 --> 44:15.821
I HAVE EVER HEARD.

44:15.854 --> 44:18.589
I'D THROW UP IF I DIDN'T LOVE
EVERY WORD OF IT.

44:22.460 --> 44:25.430
- COME ON IN, IT'S COLD.
- UH, HOLD ON.

44:25.463 --> 44:28.666
I JUST GOT TO
DO ONE LAST THING.

44:37.208 --> 44:39.277
THERE.

44:43.014 --> 44:45.984
[electronic music]

44:46.017 --> 44:53.959
*

46:19.077 --> 46:21.913
- I'M SURPRISED
TO SEE YOU HERE.

46:21.947 --> 46:24.916
- I WANTED TO ASK YOU
A QUESTION.

46:26.117 --> 46:28.887
WHY DID YOU APOLOGIZE?

46:28.920 --> 46:31.522
- WELL, I GUESS
I MISS YOU.

46:35.994 --> 46:39.564
- DO YOU STILL LOVE ME?

46:39.597 --> 46:42.067
- ALWAYS HAVE.

46:44.936 --> 46:48.573
ALWAYS WILL.

46:48.606 --> 46:51.242
- SO DO I.

46:53.544 --> 46:55.613
- SAID YOU LOOK LIKE YOU
NEED A FRIEND TO TALK TO,

46:55.646 --> 46:59.250
SO DO I.

46:59.284 --> 47:02.387
- ISN'T THERE A HOTLINE
FOR THAT?

47:02.420 --> 47:05.190
- IN A PINCH, YOU'LL DO.

47:05.223 --> 47:07.993
MY DATE WAS A BUST.

47:10.095 --> 47:12.363
- WHAT WENT WRONG?

47:14.099 --> 47:17.035
- YOU COULD SAY I DIDN'T
MAKE THE CUT.

47:18.436 --> 47:20.405
- YOU'LL LIVE.

47:23.274 --> 47:25.276
- YEAH, I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DO IT.

47:25.310 --> 47:27.946
YOU ALWAYS KNOW
THE RIGHT THING TO SAY.

47:27.979 --> 47:30.848
- [laughs]

47:32.918 --> 47:34.485
- GET YOU A DRINK?

47:34.519 --> 47:36.955
- THAT'S VERY THOUGHTFUL
OF YOU, THEODORE.

47:36.988 --> 47:39.157
DON'T MIND IF I DO.

47:39.190 --> 47:43.494
GET YOURSELF ONE OF THOSE
GIRLY THINGS YOU LIKE SO MUCH.

47:43.528 --> 47:45.363
ON ME.

47:45.396 --> 47:46.965
- THANKS, BRI.

47:46.998 --> 47:50.635
- ANYTHING...

47:50.668 --> 47:53.404
FOR A FRIEND.

47:53.438 --> 48:01.412
*
